   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-accepting-acceptted" mid="449" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="404"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>……That's bad. But why did Shalica follow you in the first place? ……Something's amiss.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-1-" mid="450" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="406"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>………………………………….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-a" mid="451" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="407"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Shalica seems reckless but she always acts based on careful thoughts.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-b" mid="452" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="408"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>She only takes action when she is certain. She didn't need to go to the island in the first place, yet she offered come along…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-c" mid="453" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="409"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Could it be…… Come to think of it, Shalica told me not to be surprised no matter what happened in Phantom Forest…!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-d" mid="454" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="410"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>That confirms that Shalica went there with a plan. But that doesn't mean offering herself as a hostage was a good thing to do.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-e" mid="455" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="411"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What should we do now…? We can't just sit around and do nothing until Shalica is done with her plan.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-f" mid="456" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="412"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Of course. We should do what we can. Hirendel wouldn't kill or harm his hostage. It would be good if we can make Chiron Island safe enough for her to investigate freely.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-g" mid="457" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="413"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>That means we should drive Hirendel out of the island. That should be done not by Merca, but Anti-Goddess Faction. Vernicka should use the peace treaty with Hirendel as a tool to keep other Childs away.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-h" mid="458" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="414"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Because Shalica would be in danger if Merca officially announces to oppose Hirendel. Am I right?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2" mid="459" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="415"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Norfe smiles.)</FONT> <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, you're becoming more and more reliable.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-2" image="QN_Vernicka" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2-" mid="460" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="416"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Vernicka should have reached the same conclusion by now. I'll take care of Grele so can you go and talk to <FONT color=#a82424>Vernicka</FONT>?/html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-a" mid="461" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="417"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka is staring blankly into space with his cold eyes.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-b" mid="462" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="418"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>…You must have reported to Anti-Goddess Faction about every single minute detail about what happened.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-c" mid="463" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="419"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>…… (How did he know...) Lord Norfe would like to express his heartfelt sympathy for what happened.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-d" mid="464" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="420"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>Anyone can say that. I believe he has told you something more useful other than that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-e" mid="465" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="421"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Tell him about Norfe's thoughts and suggestion.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-f" mid="466" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="422"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>He could be right. Shalica could have expected this to happen. It is true that the peace treaty can buy some time for Merca's safety.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-g" mid="467" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="423"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>But there was no need for her to put herself in such grave danger. There must have been another way. Yet the Anti-Goddess Faction is placing all its faith in Shalica's abilities and only looks on the bright side. Of course! It's not their own damn issue!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-h" mid="468" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="424"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>………I apologise for that. I hope you won't report such personal grumblings to Lord Norfe too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-i" mid="469" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="425"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I'm with Anti-Goddess Faction but Shalica is also my friend. I understand how you feel.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-j" mid="470" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="426"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>……I'm grateful that Shalica earned some time for Merca's Heart but I am torn between deciding what to protect.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-k" mid="471" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="427"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>I vowed to protect Merca for her sake in the first place, but now I have to put her life at risk to save the city.<BR>It would have been better if I was taken hostage instead and made her return to her rightful place… That would have made everything perfect.......</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-l" mid="472" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="428"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I disagree. You heard what Shalica said. You're someone who is good at keeping your place, but she said can't be such a leader.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-m" mid="473" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="429"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>She said you should split roles and do what you can do best. Shalica knew that you're the one who could protect the people of Merca and the leader they could trust when the city was in danger.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-n" mid="474" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="430"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I hope you will have faith in Shalica too.<BR>Anti-Goddess Faction and I will focus all our attention on saving her for now. You should protect Merca until Shalica is back.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-o" mid="475" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="431"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>…………Your tongue seems to be becoming slicker by the day. Are you taking speech classes in Mistland?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-p" mid="476" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="432"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(My tongue doesn't feel any different...)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-q" mid="477" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="433"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>Merca's Heart won't do nothing. Behind the peace treaty, we will make preparations to fight Hirendel too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-r" mid="478" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="434"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>……!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-s" mid="479" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="435"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>I must emphasise that it would only be done internally and who goes to battle officially with Hirendel would be the Anti-Goddess Faction.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-s" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-t" mid="480" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="436"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>In return, Merca will accept Rhadames refugees with open arms. Merca's people are open to changes and when the refugees arrive, Anti-Goddess Faction's ideas will spread like wildfire and prepare the groundworks for an independence from Childs.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-t" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-u" mid="481" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="437"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Thank you. I'm sure Lord Norfe will accept this suggestion.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-u" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-v" mid="482" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="438"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>I hope so.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-v" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-w" mid="483" select_type="4" />
      <talk_question mid="439"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Completed$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-w" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-" mid="484" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="440"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>I should write a formal letter to Lord Norfe soon. The moment Shalica comes back, Merca's Heart and Anti-Goddess Faction will become each other's strongest ally.<BR><BR>* You have completed Extra Chapter 7. [Facing the Enemy].</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
